entry.value: create external table if not exists ${hive_db_name}.${hive_table_name} ROW FORMAT SERDE 'org.apache.hadoop.hive.serde2.avro.AvroSerDe' STORED AS INPUTFORMAT 'org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.io.avro.AvroContainerInputFormat' OUTPUTFORMAT 'org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.io.avro.AvroContainerOutputFormat' location ${hive_external_location} TBLPROPERTIES('avro.schema.literal' = '${avro.schema}')
Assuming the table is already created as the count is greater than 1
